---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Poetry & Calligraphy" description="Discover the art of Chinese poetry and calligraphy - Tang dynasty verses, Song lyrics, and the meditative practice of brush writing">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/calligraphy-brush.jpg"
        alt="Chinese calligraphy brush writing"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1a1a1a]/95 to-[#26619C]/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#D4AF37] mb-4">LITERATURE</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-6">Poetry & Calligraphy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
          Where words become art. Tang poetry's grace, Song lyrics' depth, and the meditative practice of brush and ink.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Poetry Introduction -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#FFFEF7]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#C41E3A] mb-4">THE ART OF WORDS</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">Poetry as a Way of Life</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 mb-8">
          In ancient China, poetry was not merely literature — it was a required skill for civil service exams, a form of social currency among the elite, and a spiritual practice for cultivation of the self.
        </p>
        <div class="p-8 bg-[#26619C]/5 rounded-2xl border border-[#26619C]/20">
          <p class="font-display text-2xl italic text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed">
            "静夜思<br/>
            床前明月光<br/>
            疑是地上霜<br/>
            举头望明月<br/>
            低头思故乡"
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#26619C] mt-4 font-semibold">— Li Bai, "Quiet Night Thought"</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Major Poets -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {[
          {
            name: 'Li Bai',
            dynasty: 'Tang Dynasty',
            years: '701-762',
            desc: 'The "Immortal Banished from Earth." Known for romantic, transcendent verses that capture nature\'s grandeur.',
            work: '"Climbing High," "Quiet Night Thought"',
            color: 'bg-blue-600'
          },
          {
            name: 'Du Fu',
            dynasty: 'Tang Dynasty',
            years: '712-770',
            desc: 'The "Sage of Poetry." His works span personal grief to political commentary, reflecting turbulent times.',
            work: '"Three Officers," "Spring Prospect"',
            color: 'bg-indigo-600'
          },
          {
            name: 'Su Shi',
            dynasty: 'Song Dynasty',
            years: '1037-1101',
            desc: 'A polymath poet, painter, calligrapher, and statesman. Known for ci (lyric poetry) and philosophical depth.',
            work: '"Red Cliffs," "Mid-Autumn"',
            color: 'bg-cyan-600'
          },
          {
            name: 'Li Qingzhao',
            dynasty: 'Song Dynasty',
            years: '1084-1155',
            desc: 'The greatest female poet in Chinese history. Her ci poetry captures love, loss, and longing with delicate precision.',
            work: '"Remembrance of Twin Sisters"',
            color: 'bg-teal-600'
          }
        ].map(poet => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class={`h-3 ${poet.color}`}></div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#1a1a1a]">{poet.name}</h3>
                  <span class="text-stone-500 text-sm">{poet.dynasty}, {poet.years}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-xl">📜</div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">{poet.desc}</p>
              <div class="pt-4 border-t border-stone-100">
                <span class="text-sm text-stone-500">Famous works: </span>
                <span class="text-sm text-[#26619C]">{poet.work}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Calligraphy Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-[#D4AF37] mb-4">THE ART OF THE BRUSH</span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-white mb-6">Chinese Calligraphy</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-stone-400 mb-6">
            Calligraphy (书法, shūfǎ) is considered one of the highest art forms in Chinese culture. More than mere writing, it is a meditation in motion — the dance of brush, ink, water, and paper.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { name: 'Zhuan Shu (篆书)', desc: 'Seal script, ancient and formal, used for seals and official documents' },
              { name: 'Li Shu (隶书)', desc: 'Official script, with squared strokes and distinctive horizontal flair' },
              { name: 'Kai Shu (楷书)', desc: 'Regular script, the most readable and widely used today' },
              { name: 'Xing Shu (行书)', desc: 'Running script, flowing between regular and cursive' },
              { name: 'Cao Shu (草书)', desc: 'Grass script, highly stylized and expressive' }
            ].map(style => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-stone-800/50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#26619C] mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">{style.name}</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">{style.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/images/calligraphy-brush.jpg"
            alt="Chinese calligraphy art"
            class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-[#26619C] text-white p-6 rounded-lg">
            <div class="stat-number text-3xl mb-1">4</div>
            <div class="text-sm tracking-wide">Treasures of the Study</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#26619C] to-[#1a1a1a]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Continue Your Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-8">
        Explore more pillars of Chinese culture: philosophy, martial arts, and history.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-[#26619C] font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-100 transition-colors">
          Back to Home
        </a>
        <a href="/martial" class="px-6 py-3 border border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          Explore Martial Arts
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
